 <purpose>
   <p>
     This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the
     representation of a coordinating relationship between a two dimensional geometric model 
     and a three dimensional geometric model.
   </p>
 </purpose>

 <!-- Items in scope -->
 <inscope>
   <li>
   relationship of a geometric model in a two dimensional coordinate system to
   a geometric model in a three dimensional coordinate system 
   through the application of a geometric transformation.
   </li>
 </inscope>

